name: Colorful Cow Pattern
description:
This artwork, from the now 12 year old artist IWannaBeACOW, is her first for 2022.  She lives in a rural area in the mid-western United States.

The young artist has no Twitter yet, so please contact her art mentor, Lily White, @rblbab with any questions or comments.  Thank you!

Hand drawn cow pattern with computer added background.
